    "content": "## Aider\n- Added GPT-5, Grok-4, Gemini Flash Lite, Kimi-K2 support\n- `/clear` prints confirmation, `/undo` output simplified\n## Hugging Face\n- Introducing Storage Buckets on the Hugging Face Hub\n## OpenAI SDK\n- Custom voices, API updates, Sora improvements, ComputerTool class\n- GPT-5.4, tool search, new computer tool, add phase, websockets\n- Container network_policy, skills, images in batch API, hosted shell\n## Claude Code\n- Added MCP elicitation, ElicitationResult hooks, display name flag\n- Worktree sparsePaths, pass confirmed on inline comments\n- Actionable /context suggestions, autoMemoryDirectory, fixed memory leak\n- ModelOverrides setting, actionable SSL guidance, fixed freezes\n- Tool search bypass, `/copy` write key, optional `/plan` argument\n- `/loop` command, cron scheduling tools, voice pushToTalk rebindable\n- Bash auto-approval allowlist, fixed API 400 errors, fixed empty responses\n- `/claude-api` skill, Ctrl+U exit bash, numeric keypad support\n- Optional `/remote-control` name, Opus defaults medium effort\n- Re-introduced \"ultrathink\" keyword, removed Opus 4/4.1\n## Last Week in AI\n- Podcast: Nemotron Super, xAI reborn, Anthropic Lawsuit, Research\n- Podcast: Anthropic sues Trump, xAI starting over, Iran AI fakes\n- Podcast: GPT 5.4, Gemini Flash Lite, Supply Chain Risk\n## Ollama\n- Improved OpenClaw performance, cloud models reliability\n- Up to 2x faster Kimi-K2.5, improved tool calling accuracy\n- Ollama provider in OpenClaw, thinking levels interpreted\n- Add context length for compaction\n## Anthropic SDK\n- GA thinking-display-setting, fixed 413/529 errors\n- Propagate container_id, use filtered messages list, change array_format\n- Add MCP tools/prompts/resources helpers, add top-level cache control\n- Fix shared UserLocation, add backward-compat aliases\n- Make new tool versions available, claude-sonnet-4-6 released\n- Fix spec errors, remove speed from messages, enabling fast-mode\n- Release Claude Opus, adaptive thinking, structured outputs support\n- Migrate output_config, custom JSON encoder\n## Latent Space\n- Context Drought, Aspirations for LLMs, Retrieval After RAG\n- Replit Agent 4, Yann LeCun\u2019s AMI Labs, NVIDIA's AI Engineers\n- Autoresearch: Recursive Self Improvement\n## Gemini CLI\n- Fix docs, rename 'return' to 'enter', restrict npm bundling\n- Override toolRegistry, footer items spaced, clarify global policy\n- Fix patch versions, add chat resume footer, bold/styles in svg snapshots\n- Increase A2A agent timeout, standardize focus colors\n- Parse raw ASCII buffer strings, fix github PAT for automated PRs\n- Whitelist TERM/COLORTERM, fix billing overage, expand paste placeholders\n- Overhaul thinking UI, unify Ctrl+O hint experience"
  }
